subject: Please do assess Wikipedia
text:
This project is GREAT and long overdue: congratulations for making it, and especially for making it free :-)

I'm the Executive Director of the Wikimedia Foundation, the non-profit that operates Wikipedia and its sister projects. We've just revamped our TOU to make it more explicit and easier to understand for readers and editors: you can find the human-readable summary here http://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Terms_of_Use and the full TOU here http://wikimediafoundation.org/wiki/Terms_of_Use_(2012)/en#Our_Terms_of_Use.

Please do rate us. We aim to be highly transparent and trustworthy and we value user control and privacy: we'd be interested in your feedback. If you've got questions about anything that's not covered in the TOU, send me mail and I'll try to get you an answer.

Thanks,
Sue
